artworks.title: Raak - New Markings
artworks.desc:
Was playing with my design, and acquired some new markings. They serve as a warning - beware being caught up in a venomous bat's wings...


My bat self's ref sheet: Raak

artworks.title: Lounging by the Pool
artworks.desc:
Whoops, looks like it wasn't just rubber that I was turning into a normal rubber creature, I went all the way into a pooltoy!  At least now I get to look natural as I lay by the pool, might have to go in for a float later.

Another wonderful piece I got from  angrboda
